Hey, lady, take a look.

00:13:06.910 --> 00:13:07.650
Restaurant opening.

00:13:07.750 --> 00:13:08.460
50 off 100.

00:13:08.630 --> 00:13:09.820
Scan the QR code on it.

00:13:10.550 --> 00:13:11.530
50 off 100!

00:13:14.870 --> 00:13:16.010
My method

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:17.610
can ruin him.

00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:18.980
He'll leave in disgrace,

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.700
and even lose his family.

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:39.820
I've sent you an email.

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:40.650
Check it out.

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:42.420
Got it.

00:13:43.540 --> 00:13:45.080
[Zhou Yu'an's outsourced employee resume]

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:45.890
What's this about?

00:13:46.390 --> 00:13:47.530
You're a headhunter.

00:13:47.600 --> 00:13:48.250
You have info.

00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:49.980
Help me check this person.

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:51.370
See what she did before.

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:52.530
Who is she?

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:53.700
Why check her?

00:13:54.150 --> 00:13:54.940
Just check, okay?

00:13:55.150 --> 00:13:56.130
We'll talk when we meet.

00:14:03.340 --> 00:14:04.740
[Name: Zhou Yu'an, Position Applied: Admin Assistant]

00:14:04.750 --> 00:14:06.060
Zhou Yu'an...

00:14:20.200 --> 00:14:20.820
My method can ruin him.

00:14:20.840 --> 00:14:22.250
He'll leave in disgrace,

00:14:22.270 --> 00:14:23.980
and even lose his family.

00:14:35.790 --> 00:14:37.220
You don't need to drive instead of me.

00:14:38.910 --> 00:14:40.650
I didn't want you to get tired.

00:14:41.720 --> 00:14:42.940
Then drive carefully.

00:14:43.550 --> 00:14:43.940
Look,

00:14:43.960 --> 00:14:45.060
if you run into a Benz,

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:46.060
can you stay away from it?

00:14:46.150 --> 00:14:47.580
Why should I?

00:14:48.270 --> 00:14:49.490
He cut me off first!

00:14:49.670 --> 00:14:51.340
So you have to pass him?

00:14:52.200 --> 00:14:53.580
Fine, it's no big deal.

00:14:55.870 --> 00:14:56.770
Has anyone placed an order?

00:14:57.790 --> 00:14:59.180
There will be a prompt.

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.060
No orders yet?

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:05.420
We can't even cover the gas cost.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:07.700
Well, you're aware of that?

00:15:08.390 --> 00:15:09.610
Didn't you listen to the training?

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:11.420
Hurry and find a place to rest.

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:13.180
Where should I go?

00:15:15.910 --> 00:15:16.940
Wherever you need to.

00:15:24.200 --> 00:15:24.980
Still no orders?

00:15:33.440 --> 00:15:34.490
Just waiting like this?

00:15:36.790 --> 00:15:37.300
Yeah,

00:15:38.030 --> 00:15:39.250
what are we even waiting for?

00:15:39.790 --> 00:15:40.890
For a good start!

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:53.420
Why take off your shoes?

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:55.980
My feet are sore.

00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:57.060
I'm just going to massage them.

00:15:57.240 --> 00:15:58.610
Why do it here?

00:16:00.120 --> 00:16:00.770
What?

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:02.180
