00:16:02.790 --> 00:16:03.370
Why wait

00:16:03.390 --> 00:16:04.940
under a tree?

00:16:05.390 --> 00:16:05.850
Jialu,

00:16:05.870 --> 00:16:06.890
what's wrong with you?

00:16:07.910 --> 00:16:08.730
I just want to know,

00:16:08.750 --> 00:16:09.980
why a tree?

00:16:10.030 --> 00:16:11.010
A tree?

00:16:12.790 --> 00:16:13.730
Are you crazy?

00:16:13.960 --> 00:16:15.130
You want a treat?

00:16:15.150 --> 00:16:15.820
Huh?

00:16:17.270 --> 00:16:18.980
You have a new order.

00:16:19.150 --> 00:16:20.420
It's one kilometer away.

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:22.100
Please grab the order soon.

00:16:23.790 --> 00:16:24.730
Order successfully grabbed.

00:16:25.150 --> 00:16:26.730
Please arrive at the location

00:16:26.790 --> 00:16:27.580
within 10 minutes.

00:16:28.030 --> 00:16:28.940
What did I say?

00:16:29.910 --> 00:16:31.010
Isn't this the good start?

00:16:31.510 --> 00:16:32.770
Arguing with your uncle,

00:16:32.910 --> 00:16:34.060
what are we even waiting for?

00:16:35.440 --> 00:16:36.060
Wait a minute!

00:16:36.390 --> 00:16:36.890
Let's take a photo

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:37.850
and send it to Jiaqi.

00:16:38.030 --> 00:16:39.300
This is our first deal.

00:16:39.870 --> 00:16:41.420
Hurry, we'll run out of time!

00:16:57.500 --> 00:16:59.700
[Uncle]

00:17:05.620 --> 00:17:08.140
[Good luck!]

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:12.700
Wait, is this the right way?

00:17:12.750 --> 00:17:13.490
The GPS is with you.

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:14.290
Why ask me?

00:17:14.350 --> 00:17:15.980
The GPS app freezes up!

00:17:16.070 --> 00:17:16.700
Hurry,

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:17.700
pull over!

00:17:32.750 --> 00:17:33.700
Am I your uncle?

00:17:34.030 --> 00:17:34.620
What's wrong?

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:36.810
When I told you to turn left,

00:17:36.830 --> 00:17:37.770
why didn't you turn?

00:17:38.110 --> 00:17:39.860
The GPS app is frozen!

00:17:39.920 --> 00:17:41.180
What's that got to do with the GPS?

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:42.180
It's up to us!

00:17:42.270 --> 00:17:43.010
It's up to us?

00:17:43.030 --> 00:17:44.290
Then do something!

00:17:44.440 --> 00:17:45.250
I was busy driving.

00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.330
You didn't even check the GPS,

00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.250
just babbling there!

00:17:51.270 --> 00:17:51.860
What's wrong?

00:17:52.070 --> 00:17:52.940
I forgot to mention.

00:17:53.030 --> 00:17:54.700
You guys can stop by the house at lunch.

00:17:54.750 --> 00:17:55.810
I've prepared food for you.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:56.660
No need.

00:17:56.790 --> 00:17:57.380
When we're hungry,

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:58.080
we'll just find a restaurant

00:17:58.080 --> 00:17:58.660
and grab something to eat.

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:00.700
How much did you earn?

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:01.770
You're still eating out?

00:18:02.240 --> 00:18:02.770
I'll pack it for you

00:18:02.790 --> 00:18:04.010
in a thermal food box.

00:18:04.350 --> 00:18:05.900
Come pick it up.

00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:07.220
Thanks, Mom.

00:18:12.550 --> 00:18:13.490
Figured it out?

00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:23.490
Look at my judgment.

00:18:23.640 --> 00:18:24.090
Sharp, right?

00:18:24.440 --> 00:18:25.730
What's it to you?

00:18:25.790 --> 00:18:27.290
It's because of the GPS.

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:28.290
With this efficiency,

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:29.140
we can grab

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:30.490
two more orders before noon.

00:18:31.350 --> 00:18:32.330
It's been smooth.

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.010
Building 13.

00:18:39.920 --> 00:18:41.220
Didn't you say it's 10 minutes away?

00:18:41.510 --> 00:18:42.380
If you don't show up, I'll cancel it.

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:44.090
Go ahead! Don't talk to me like that!

00:18:44.550 --> 00:18:45.730
We're here, buddy!

00:18:47.310 --> 00:18:48.050
Speak nicely.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:49.490
We'll lose money if he leaves a bad review.

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:15.770
Sorry, everyone.

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:16.290
Sorry about that.

00:19:16.310 --> 00:19:17.420
Step aside.

00:19:17.790 --> 00:19:18.770
Move!

00:19:18.790 --> 00:19:19.520
Sorry.

00:19:19.520 --> 00:19:20.050
Be careful.

00:19:20.350 --> 00:19:21.290
Move the chicken coop.

00:19:21.790 --> 00:19:22.660
The car's coming.

00:19:24.240 --> 00:19:24.980
Move!

00:19:25.160 --> 00:19:26.090
Sorry.

00:19:26.160 --> 00:19:27.090
Make way.

00:19:27.240 --> 00:19:28.380
Move!

00:19:29.200 --> 00:19:30.570
Move a little to the left!

00:19:33.510 --> 00:19:34.730
What are you doing?

00:19:36.030 --> 00:19:37.140
Move!

00:19:38.030 --> 00:19:38.700
Sorry about that.

00:19:38.830 --> 00:19:39.940
Can you move this?

00:19:40.070 --> 00:19:41.530
The car's coming.

00:19:41.960 --> 00:19:42.810
Come on.

00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:43.570
Let's go.

00:19:43.960 --> 00:19:44.940
Move this side!

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:45.810
What's going on?

00:19:51.960 --> 00:19:52.940
Unbelievable!

00:20:10.710 --> 00:20:11.620
Let's go home for lunch.

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.180
All you know is eating.

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:15.940
All morning,

00:20:15.960 --> 00:20:16.980
we only earned fifty.

